a.n: Sneaking And Freaking In The Shower

p.k: Rose Monroe returns home to find her boyfriend and his brother, Charles, hanging out. Turns out Charles was kicked out of his house after getting caught cheating on his girlfriend. Rose is more than happy to give him a place to stay in the meantime, but when she is ditched by her boyfriend to go have a guys' night out, she decides she wants to have a little fun of her own.
